LLM_response_editer:
In the screen, the "Align Left" icon is located on the right side of the toolbar, which needs to be clicked in order to apply the Align Left function in the selected text, which is done in JSON format as follows:

```json
[
    {"action_type":"MouseAction","mouse_action_type":"click","mouse_button":"left","mouse_position":{"width":970,"height":100}}
]
```
